{"tid":773078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(契哥自身難保) 確認俄國人動用化武 美國對俄羅斯新一輪制裁 針對軍民兩用科技產品","createTime":"2018-08-09T09:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T01:08:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92533d9072c2a23c9fc8fc4c268d17f469b39cce","tid":773078,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"美國政府表示，俄羅斯確實與今年3月英國前雙面間諜斯克里帕爾父女（Sergei Skripal）中毒案有關，將對俄羅斯實施新一輪制裁，針對出口到俄羅斯的軍民兩用高科技產品。英國對此表示歡迎；俄羅斯則再批評各界的指控無理。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert）稱，俄羅斯策劃使用神經毒劑諾維喬克（Novichok）毒害斯克里帕爾父女，違反1991年訂立的國際法《生化武器管制和戰爭根絕法》（Chemical and Biological Weapons Control and Warfare Elimination Act），決定向俄羅斯實施新一輪制裁，下月22日正式生效。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院又向國會表示，這輪制裁只是措施的其中一部分，如俄羅斯拒絕在90日內承諾不再使用化武，以及讓調查人員實地驗證，美國就會落實第二部分制裁。<br />\n<br />\n新一輪制裁針對從美國出口到俄羅斯的軍民兩用科技產品，這類產品被美國政府視為敏感產品，一般在出口前要逐一審查。在制裁令下，預料這些產品也會全部被拒絕出口。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府對制裁令表示歡迎，稱國際間對使用化武反應強烈，不會對俄羅斯的挑釁行為視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯駐聯合國官員諷刺美國為「美利堅聯合制裁國」（United Sanctions of America），再次批評外界指控無根據和缺乏邏輯，執意將所有問題推到俄羅斯身上。<br />\n<br />\n斯克里帕爾父女3月在英國索爾茲伯里接觸神經毒劑陷入昏迷，情況一度危殆，後來康復。英國指摘俄羅斯是幕後黑手，引起一連串外交風波。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2133988/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%80%E8%BC%AA%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%20%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%BB%8D%E6%B0%91%E5%85%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2133988%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%2520%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=767bc989\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2133988/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%80%E8%BC%AA%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%20%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%BB%8D%E6%B0%91%E5%85%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81</a>"},{"pid":"0c236d8ec343660d4d6812a6cb12e8c6683ab604","tid":773078,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"美國vs 支，俄，伊朗，北韓<br />\n<br />\n歐盟食花生"},{"pid":"d9515d608d4aef521183718de9a73263f0413269","tid":773078,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c236d8ec343660d4d6812a6cb12e8c6683ab604","tid":773078,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"美國vs 支，俄，伊朗，北韓<br />\n<br />\n歐盟食花生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067cfc6d6cb5c485259252e3becd8f25ffceb82b","tid":773078,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:21:46.000Z","msg":"幾時整埋石油禁運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606a5cbe524f9c534d5fbef518b17fa80c536f48","tid":773078,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c236d8ec343660d4d6812a6cb12e8c6683ab604","tid":773078,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"美國vs 支，俄，伊朗，北韓<br />\n<br />\n歐盟食花生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"仲有澳紐加都食緊"},{"pid":"b5929cc1ca2b372e3db7ea094e9d08064c6a6b27","tid":773078,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606a5cbe524f9c534d5fbef518b17fa80c536f48","tid":773078,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c236d8ec343660d4d6812a6cb12e8c6683ab604","tid":773078